ISLAMABAD, Feb 25 (APP): Foreign Minister Makhdoom Shah Mahmood Qureshi on Friday expressed his deep grief over the sad demise of a senior politician from Balochistan Dr. Abdul Hayee Baloch.
The Foreign Minister prayed for the departed and expressed his condolences with the bereaved family.
